EN: This city has a very large clock tower.

ZH:  我们可以听到钟声从教堂传来。
EN: We can hear the bell tolling from the church.

ZH:  钟已经指向了午夜。
EN: The clock has struck midnight.

ZH:  这座城市的钟口是金色的。
EN: The face of the clock tower in this city is golden.

